 235        /*   1. Go to https://wwwn.cdc.gov/nchs/nhanes/search/datapage.aspx          */
 236        /*   2. Select cycle "August 2021 - August 2023"                             */
 237        /*   3. Download these XPT files:                                            */
 238        /*        Demographics  -> DEMO_L.XPT                                        */
 239        /*        Examination   -> BMX_L.XPT                                         */
 240        /*        Questionnaire -> PAQ_L.XPT  (2021-2023: PAD790Q/U, PAD800,        */
 241        /*                                     PAD810Q/U, PAD820, PAD680)            */
 242        /*        Dietary       -> DR1TOT_L.XPT  (Day 1 Total Nutrients)             */
 243        /*        Examination   -> BPXO_L.XPT   (Blood Pressure)                    */
 244        /*   4. Upload all five files to your SAS OnDemand home folder:              */
 245        /*        Server Files -> Upload -> select all five XPT files                */
 246        /*   5. Update %let DATAPATH above to point to that folder.                  */
 247        /******************************************************************************/
